page.title: 11THE MEADOWS CONT.
page.content: {We identified some of the plants which {grew in the local meadow.}We found:red clover,white clover,dock,corn poppy, greater plantain, chicory, nettles, creeping buttercup,dandelion, goldilocks, field bindweed,self heal daisies,greater knapweed,yarrow,bird foot trefoil,ox eye daisies,acrimony rib plantain,lady's bedstraw,spiny rest harrow,ragwort,cutleaved cranesbill,slender thistle,and white slender thistle.In a recently ploughed field we also found silver weed, creeping thistle,spear thistle, pineapple weed,salad burnet,pink campion,and nipplewort. { Under the hedges}we also found great willow herb,dog rose,yellow sow thistle,hedge parsley,wild arum,wild rose,hogweed,meadow vetchling,tufted vetch,common vetch,dog mercury,field rose,and ground ivy.
